{"tid":1777801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國足輸波 裂頭腳直踢日本球員","createTime":"2019-12-10T13:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:15:04.000Z","uid":89543,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa08da632072157f6ca5df4b58bffd15e2511478","tid":1777801,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"【中國1:2日本】<br />\n上半場30分鐘，球場上演了驚嚇的一幕，當時中國球員姜至鵬在中前場因踢人犯規，但這名國足後衞居然飛踢到日本後衞橋岡大樹的頭上，最終裁判只向姜至鵬出示黃牌。但在換邊後的70分鐘，日本透過一次角球攻勢，由三浦弦太頂入，幫助日本隊拉開比數；國足在90分鐘的唯一一次射門中框，便成功追回一球，董學升接應傳球頭槌頂入，最終日本隊仍然成功以2:1擊敗中國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WNHQFM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WNHQFM.png&h=ea7dd175&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92bf4409d2633d487654de22a077c0f52c4ff586","tid":1777801,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又柒出國際"},{"pid":"5682689a2f5c3d6df0e9009bc1dbbfcc4fd32caf","tid":1777801,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3071786937af72eb22a7f65ee129358db6d242b9","tid":1777801,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408648b7666e3d2ca7b13f3ed763c0e93392f8c6","tid":1777801,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"二十成功力？"},{"pid":"b6c9541ce8ff31022f6addeedeac15da1c3e8267","tid":1777801,"uid":305575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"中國都係同俄羅斯自己搞比賽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748a928e2090d9f8df43735e8eb094f50be27846","tid":1777801,"uid":165683,"like":1